### Hash Table

**Two-Pass:**

```java
// Two-Pass
public int[] twoSum(int[] nums, int target) {
  // map<target - num, index>
  int n = nums.length;
  // set map
  Map<Integer, Integer> map = new HashMap<>();
  for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {
    map.put(target - nums[i], i);
  }

  for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {
    int val = nums[i];
    if (map.containsKey(val)) {
      int j = map.get(val);
      if (i == j) continue;
      return new int[] { i + 1, j + 1 };
    }
  }
  throw new IllegalArgumentException();
}
```

